@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Terms of Use";
}

<section class="ul-section-head ul-enter">
    <div>
        <div class="ul-section-sub">/ Legal</div>
        <h2>📋 Terms of Use</h2>
    </div>
</section>

<div class="ul-card ul-enter" style="background:rgba(78,224,176,0.05);border-color:rgba(78,224,176,0.25);margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
    <strong style="color:var(--accent-mint);">ℹ Last updated:</strong>
    <span style="color:var(--text-mid);">May 2026</span>
</div>

<div class="ul-card ul-enter" style="margin-bottom:1rem;">
    <h3>1. Acceptance of Terms</h3>
    <p>By using the UrbanLink platform you agree to comply with these Terms of Use. If you do not agree with any of the terms, please do not use the platform.</p>
</div>

<div class="ul-card ul-enter" style="margin-bottom:1rem;">
    <h3>2. Description of the Service</h3>
    <p>UrbanLink is an online platform for ride-sharing and travel-event coordination in Bulgaria. The service includes:</p>
    <ul style="color:var(--text-mid);line-height:1.7;">
        <li>Creating and managing carpool trips between Bulgarian towns and cities</li>
        <li>Posting and joining travel events</li>
        <li>Reserving seats on trips with multiple payment methods</li>
        <li>Identity and driver verification</li>
        <li>Community chat and direct messaging between users</li>
        <li>Driver ratings after completed trips</li>
    </ul>
</div>

<div class="ul-card ul-enter" style="margin-bottom:1rem;">
    <h3>3. Registration and Account</h3>
    <p>To use the full functionality of the platform you must create an account. You are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your login credentials and for all activity performed through your account. You must be at least 18 years old to register.</p>
</div>

<div class="ul-card ul-enter" style="margin-bottom:1rem;">
    <h3>4. Code of Conduct</h3>
    <p>By using the platform you agree:</p>
    <ul style="color:var(--text-mid);line-height:1.7;">
        <li>Not to publish false or misleading information</li>
        <li>Not to infringe the rights of other users</li>
        <li>Not to use the platform for illegal purposes</li>
        <li>To maintain respectful and polite communication</li>
        <li>To honour reservations you have made and to be on time</li>
    </ul>
</div>

<div class="ul-card ul-enter" style="margin-bottom:1rem;">
    <h3>5. Driver Responsibilities</h3>
    <p>Drivers must hold a valid driver's license, have a roadworthy vehicle with valid insurance, and obey all traffic laws. UrbanLink is not responsible for incidents that occur during trips arranged through the platform.</p>
</div>

<div class="ul-card ul-enter" style="margin-bottom:1rem;">
    <h3>6. Verification</h3>
    <p>Verification of identity and driver status is performed by platform administrators. Approval grants you additional privileges (e.g. ability to create trips, send messages, make reservations). Submitted documents are stored only until reviewed and are wiped from the database after a decision.</p>
</div>

<div class="ul-card ul-enter" style="margin-bottom:1rem;">
    <h3>7. Limitation of Liability</h3>
    <p>UrbanLink acts as a marketplace connecting drivers and passengers. We are not a transport provider and bear no responsibility for the actions of users, the condition of vehicles, or the outcome of any trip.</p>
</div>

<div class="ul-card ul-enter">
    <h3>8. Changes to the Terms</h3>
    <p>We may update these Terms from time to time. Continued use of the platform after such changes constitutes acceptance of the updated Terms.</p>
</div>
